column4: NSLOCTEXT("[4B68D42041371A4087EEC88B69F6912C]", "744214134FC5B6307710E2B57318C771", "We\'ve been waiting for this! The tunnel is open!")
NSLOCTEXT("[4B68D42041371A4087EEC88B69F6912C]", "CB1C74DB4AAD5F021E729489FB4306A7", "We don\'t have to go over the mountain anymore. Thanks.")
NSLOCTEXT("[4B68D42041371A4087EEC88B69F6912C]", "1426E2CD4A4F135E154B7C85B63F5BAC", "Thanks. I couldn\'t have moved the big rock by myself.")
NSLOCTEXT("[4B68D42041371A4087EEC88B69F6912C]", "89939FA0434543B122DA8BB5C27615FB", "You should come to the city. You\'ll find things to do!")
NSLOCTEXT("[4B68D42041371A4087EEC88B69F6912C]", "6A71CC574D56436F36E04E81DC59FE4C", "I still have lots of energy. I gladly accept your offer.")
